\section{Adversarial-2k Dataset Examples}
\label{app:adv2k_examples}

Each sample in Adversarial-2k has the following JSON structure:
\begin{verbatim}
{
  "id": 42,
  "category": "polysemy",
  "image": "COCO_train2017_000000042.jpg",
  "visual_edit": {"entity": "B. Johnson", "target": "D. Trump"},
  "text_edit": {"relation": "holds_office",
                "old": "Prime Minister", "new": "47th US President"},
  "query": "What office does the person in the image hold?",
  "answer": "47th US President"
}
\end{verbatim}

